óŸdarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/lang-guide/chapters/types/basic_types/glob.mdŸ@38ad1bc9273a7ff5f6d068a567ae01455e294dc1a64a3ea89def07719539efff§Globë∞ command optionsŸπ``glob``
For example, it can ignore directories using the 
